      "113. Bosin Airplane Co. Plant 2. Scattie.",
      "Dear Nahl Yours of 15th at hand\nand will answer next few days- but\nI still have the copy of 9W45 on hand\nit is supberb in every respect- Pi\nsigned, pilot and co-pilot signed.\n2 pieces only known, according to suel\ninformation available at time of\nthe flight. Albert N Brown 270 Tehams\nSan Francisco\nSAN FRAN\n102\nS\n1/143\n517 West St\nStillwater\nOkla\nP C Nahl\nNSE\nBUY"
